  <brief_title>A Study to Evaluate the Safety and Efficacy of Three Doses of a Controlled Release Formulation of Varenicline for Smoking Cessation</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 2, Seven Week, Double-Blind, Placebo Controlled, Randomized, Parallel Group Study To Evaluate The Safety And Efficacy Of Three Doses Of A Controlled Release Formulation Of Varenicline For Smoking Cessation</official_title>
