  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the safety, efficacy, and tolerability of twice
      daily (BID) administration of three dose strengths (1.2 mg, 1.8 mg, and 2.4 mg) of
      varenicline controlled release (CR) tablets in adult smokers.
    </textblock>
